<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>JESUH KAN HAWI THA BIK A SI CH307</title>
<key>F</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Kannih kan sual sifah ingtu, Kan hawi Jesuh a si lai, Pathian sinah
 kan duh vialte Hal ah cun a tha dah ngai, Hna-ngamnak tampi um loin,
 Fahnak ngaihchiatnak kan huah, Kan duh vialte Pathian sinah, Hal loin kan
 um caah.

[V2]
 Fahnak le tukforh kan huah maw, Hna-hnawhnak in kan um dah? Kan lung
 belte rawk hin hlah seh, Pathian sinah thlacam u, Sifah huahnak kha an
 chanhtu, Hawi khuazei ah na hmu maw, Kan ngaih-chiatnak kha Jesuh hngal,
 Pathian sinah thlacam u.

[V3]
 Zaang ngei lomi kan si cio maw, Kan thil kha a rit tuk dah? Asungmi
 kan Khamhtu Jesuh, A ngaih lai, kan hal tikah. Kan hawi nih an kan hlawt
 ahcun, Pathian Bawi sinah chim u, Akut in an lak an pom lai, Hna-ngamnak
 kan hmuh lai ta.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>307</hymn_number>
</song>